<subSubSection id="4E90094348F99DFC7FC4B128866E5709" pageId="9" pageNumber="224" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="0D560E6645A5B19DD909D49CCA11CE14" pageId="9" pageNumber="224">Distribution, phenology and biology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E8E3A4EE2D4B4C8545380A7B73DB36D0" pageId="9" pageNumber="224">
Recorded only for the DRC and Tanzania. While there is no certainty regarding the precise type locality, the coordinates of the nearest settlement (Kambove) serve to indicate its presence in the DRC (
<figureCitation id="B83D3C41FCACEEA6359DEE510FB5BD96" captionStart="Figure 25" captionStartId="F14" captionText="Figure 25. Distribution of Astochia species: A. africana, A. armata, A. neavensis." figureDoi="10.3897/AfrInvertebr.60.38432.figure25" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/346349" pageId="9" pageNumber="224" tableDoi="10.3897/AfrInvertebr.60.38432.figure25">Fig. 25</figureCitation>
). Collected in October and November (Table 
<tableCitation id="A9E5936F3BA75D940F6E317E9D3ACDC7" captionStartId="T1" httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/77ABE6B430CB8ADF8FCB922543B38124" pageId="9" pageNumber="224" tableUuid="77ABE6B430CB8ADF8FCB922543B38124">1</tableCitation>
). No biological information is available.
</paragraph>
